{"tid":1642563,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"警察戒嚴後就出老解","createTime":"2019-10-09T18:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T01:19:18.000Z","uid":80972,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"410c630e564aa1efc8c3ccad7b7a8e965701facd","tid":1642563,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:30:44.000Z","msg":"明居正8月尾講會警察戒嚴<br />\n而家黨鐵日日早收，狗隊晚晚出黎捉人、兇細路同街坊，已經中左警察戒嚴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dc7vT4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDc7vT4J.jpg&h=b3cb5450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JmT7tcmI3Mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJmT7tcmI3Mo&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX560IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=3eee77d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JmT7tcmI3Mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日又無啦啦炒左架老解車，如果過2日又見到老解起街唔知做乜Q的，應該都係準備變成武警/老解戒嚴。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191009&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60133262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191009%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60133262&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX560IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=67beb288\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191009%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60133262&h=9caf6689\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191009&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60133262</a>"},{"pid":"a85da7dfe3f925c92eab2eff3df721b286e26241","tid":1642563,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:36:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc1407a0bf3c729910ab052cb5e1b8e24ef6a96f","tid":1642563,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:36:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c04726e4954dc777a0754e2c99d539871f806d22","tid":1642563,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:42:45.000Z","msg":"大陸支那畜小蝗蟲<br />\n3歲就